<h1>Pane</h1>

<p>The pane components are used unside a window to present horizontal content.</p>

<h2>Splash Layout</h2>

<p>The splash layouts pane will position content in the middle of the window. This layout is also perfect for using a splash image for the background.</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="splash-layout"}}

    {{#uxs-window image="https://placeimg.com/2560/1600/any/grayscale"}}
      {{#uxs-pane splash=true}}
        {{uxs-subheading "Splash"}}
      {{/uxs-pane}}
    {{/uxs-window}}

  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet "splash-layout.hbs"}}

{{/docs-demo}}

<h2>Single Layout</h2>

<p>The single layout places content in one large padded pane.</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="single-layout"}}

    {{#uxs-window}}
      {{#uxs-pane single=true class="bg-p5"}}
        {{uxs-subheading "Single"}}
      {{/uxs-pane}}
    {{/uxs-window}}

  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet "single-layout.hbs"}}

{{/docs-demo}}

<h2>Two Column Layout</h2>

<p>The main pane will take up 2/3 of the window width a side pane taking up the rest.</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="two-col-layout"}}

    {{#uxs-window}}
      {{#uxs-pane main=true class="bg-p5"}}
        {{uxs-subheading "Main"}}
      {{/uxs-pane}}
      {{#uxs-pane aside=true class="bg-p4"}}
        {{uxs-subheading "Aside"}}
      {{/uxs-pane}}
    {{/uxs-window}}

  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet "two-col-layout.hbs"}}

{{/docs-demo}}

<h2>Three Column Layout</h2>

<p>Three even panes 1/3 of the window width.</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="three-col-layout"}}

    {{#uxs-window}}
      {{#uxs-pane index=true class="bg-p5"}}
        {{uxs-subheading "Index"}}
      {{/uxs-pane}}
      {{#uxs-pane detail=true class="bg-p4"}}
        {{uxs-subheading "Detail"}}
      {{/uxs-pane}}
      {{#uxs-pane aside=true class="bg-p3"}}
        {{uxs-subheading "Aside"}}
      {{/uxs-pane}}
    {{/uxs-window}}

  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet "three-col-layout.hbs"}}

{{/docs-demo}}
